# ============================================================================
# Homelab .gitignore
# Prevents committing secrets, credentials, kubeconfigs, and machine-specific
# generated state to version control.
# ============================================================================

## Kubernetes secrets / credentials
kubeconfig
kubeconfig.yaml
*.kubeconfig
admin.conf
**/pki/
**/*.key
**/*.crt
!diagrams/**/*.key      # (guard in case a diagram export ever uses .key ext)
join-command.txt
kubeadm-join.sh.generated

## SSH keys
id_rsa
id_rsa.pub
id_ed25519
id_ed25519.pub
*.pem

## Environment / secret files
.env
.env.*
*.secret
secrets.yaml

## Terraform (future roadmap items)
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.backup
.terraform/
.terraform.lock.hcl

## Ansible (future roadmap items)
*.retry
vault.yml

## Proxmox backups
*.vma
*.vma.zst
*.vma.gz

## OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
.vscode/
.idea/

## Logs
*.log
logs/

## Samba
smb.conf.bak

## Local scratch / test output
tmp/
scratch/
